snippet.title: The Great Tsunami: Italian Global Game Jam 2017
snippet.description:
Ride the wave and help our hero Tsunami to rid the sea by monsters of Japanese mythology!
The game is totally hand designed and fully developed in 48 hours during the Global Game Jam 2017! (Politecnico di Milano, Italy)

Available on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.OutGame.TheGreatTsunami

Windows Store: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/the-great-tsunami/9nxgmqddbbjm

WebGL: https://outgame.itch.io/the-great-tsunami
